  "detail": "standard",
  "metadata": {
    "platform": "loom",
    "title": "Boost In-App Demo Video",
    "duration": 175,
    "durationFormatted": "2:55",
    "url": "https://www.loom.com/share/bdebdfe44b294225ac718bad241a94fe"
  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "time": "0:01",
      "text": "Hi, I'm Josh Owens co-founder of boost.",
      "endTime": "0:03",
      "speaker": "1"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:04",
      "text": "Boost is super easy for students to download it's free in the app store.",
      "endTime": "0:07"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:07",
      "text": "And after a few details on how to use boost, we ask a student",
      "endTime": "0:10"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:10",
      "text": "to select their school and log in using their canvas credentials.",
      "endTime": "0:13"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:13",
      "text": "After that boost is good to go for the rest of the semester,",
      "endTime": "0:16"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:16",
      "text": "students get assignment notifications sent directly to their phone,",
      "endTime": "0:19"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:19",
      "text": "reminding them of what they have not yet submitted increasing assignment ins and grades.",
      "endTime": "0:24"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:24",
      "text": "The app is easy for students and parents to use.",
      "endTime": "0:27"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:27",
      "text": "The first tab shows boosts sent to the students vote.",
      "endTime": "0:29"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:30",
      "text": "The second tab, let's say student, add their own work or events that start",
      "endTime": "0:33"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:33",
      "text": "on canvas. And the third tab is the planner,",
      "endTime": "0:36"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:36",
      "text": "which shows upcoming assignments by class and details on how to complete them.",
      "endTime": "0:40"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:41",
      "text": "If a student clicks on an assignment in the planner,",
      "endTime": "0:44"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:45",
      "text": "it sends them to the direct canvas link to get more information on the",
      "endTime": "0:48"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:48",
      "text": "assignment or to complete the work as needed if that is available for them.",
      "endTime": "0:52"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:53",
      "text": "So the integration to canvas is seamless for a student and boost makes it",
      "endTime": "0:57"
    },
    {
      "time": "0:57",
      "text": "easy for a student to not just see what needs to be done,",
      "endTime": "1:00"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:00",
      "text": "but also go directly to the work, to complete it on time.",
      "endTime": "1:03"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:10",
      "text": "If we go back to the notification tab,",
      "endTime": "1:12",
      "speaker": "1"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:13",
      "text": "you can see details on the notification sent to the student's phone,",
      "endTime": "1:17"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:18",
      "text": "and the notifications are linked to assignments in canvas via the planner.",
      "endTime": "1:22"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:22",
      "text": "So students can get right to work without searching for what is needed to",
      "endTime": "1:26"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:26",
      "text": "turn in. Sometimes students have",
      "endTime": "1:31"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:31",
      "text": "things they need to turn in on their own, and one reminders for that",
      "endTime": "1:34"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:34",
      "text": "as well. That's why we've included the add activity tab.",
      "endTime": "1:37"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:38",
      "text": "So students can keep track of all the things they need to get done,",
      "endTime": "1:41"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:41",
      "text": "whether the instructor has put it into canvas or not.",
      "endTime": "1:44"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:44",
      "text": "And we give students the ability to set reminders on these items,",
      "endTime": "1:48"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:48",
      "text": "just like the assignment data we pull directly from canvas,",
      "endTime": "1:51"
    },
    {
      "time": "1:56",
      "text": "And that activity then gets added to the student's planner in boost with their",
      "endTime": "2:00"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:00",
      "text": "preferences set. So they don't miss any work,",
      "endTime": "2:02"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:03",
      "text": "whether it's in canvas or not.",
      "endTime": "2:04"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:12",
      "text": "Finally in the top, right of this is the settings tab here.",
      "endTime": "2:16",
      "speaker": "1"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:16",
      "text": "Students can set their individual preferences for notifications sent to their phone,",
      "endTime": "2:20"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:21",
      "text": "and we let them set those preferences by class and by notification type.",
      "endTime": "2:24"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:25",
      "text": "So they can make sure to get exactly the help they need to succeed",
      "endTime": "2:28"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:28",
      "text": "when they need it. And for the classes that they need it for.",
      "endTime": "2:31"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:33",
      "text": "We also include privacy statements, student help,",
      "endTime": "2:36"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:36",
      "text": "and an FAQ right here for students to reference.",
      "endTime": "2:38"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:38",
      "text": "If they get confused about using boost",
      "endTime": "2:40"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:46",
      "text": "And they can even email us directly@helpatboost.education from the app,",
      "endTime": "2:51",
      "speaker": "1"
    },
    {
      "time": "2:51",
      "text": "if they run into any issues, that's boost",
      "endTime": "2:54"
    }
  ],
